Senate Resolution 353
By: Senators Goodman of the 8th, Summers of the 13th, Watson of the 11th, Echols of the
49th, Hickman of the 4th and others
A RESOLUTION
1 Congratulating the Valdosta State University football team for winning the 2024 Gulf South
2 Conference Championship, the Super Region Two Title, and reaching the NCAA Division
3 II National Championship Game; and for other purposes.
4 WHEREAS, Valdosta State University is nationally known for its tradition of athletic and
5 academic excellence, having won nine national championships and 57 Gulf South
6 Conference titles in multiple sports, as well as having numerous athletes win Academic
7 All-Conference and Academic All-American titles; and
8
9 WHEREAS, The 2024 Valdosta State football team won the program's 11th Gulf South
10 Conference Championship, marking the most of any school in Gulf South Conference
11 history; and
12 WHEREAS, the Blazers reached the national championship game for the seventh time in
13 program history and third time since 2018, while the seven appearances in the title game are
14 second-most all-time in NCAA Division II history; and
15 WHEREAS, the Valdosta State University football team has established and maintained a
16 proud tradition of excellence with equal emphases on character and academics; and
